This software assumes a standard gcc toolchain.

Please also ensure that gsl is installed: https://www.gnu.org/software/gsl/

$ make all

    Builds the library, creating the ./mainc and ./mainc.opt binaries
    and runs a small test.

    Run ./main.out.opt for usage.

$ make test

    Runs each sampler on the distributions in the directory d/ (~20 seconds).

    The total runtime needed to generate one million samples and the number of
    PRNG calls is printed to stdout.
